            <li styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-11px; margin-top:8px; margin-right:4px; margin-bottom:8px; margin-left:11px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:117px left ;"><text styleclass="Table font Warning_1">Make sure operators know the locations of all the &quot;Emergency Stop&quot; switches prior to performing machine operation or maintenance to enable use in an abnormal or dangerous situation</text><text styleclass="Table font Warning_3">.</text></li>
          </list>
